s.", "tokens": [50546, 1449, 312, 14618, 300, 436, 434, 406, 410, 7981, 604, 295, 641, 17203, 13, 50740], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12143798540997248, "compression_ratio": 1.580188679245283, "no_speech_prob": 0.06357917189598083}, {"id": 20, "seek": 10348, "start": 111.0, "end": 118.2, "text": " Now the purpose of this exercise is for them to not step forward into your bubble, your", "tokens": [50740, 823, 264, 4334, 295, 341, 5380, 307, 337, 552, 281, 406, 1823, 2128, 666, 428, 12212, 11, 428, 51100], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12143798540997248, "compression_ratio": 1.580188679245283, "no_speech_prob": 0.06357917189598083}, {"id": 21, "seek": 10348, "start": 118.2, "end": 119.2, "text": " energy bubble.", "tokens": [51100, 2281, 12212, 13, 51150], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12143798540997248, "compression_ratio": 1.580188679245283, "no_speech_prob": 0.06357917189598083}, {"id": 22, "seek": 10348, "start": 119.2, "end": 126.0, "text": " So you see me not moving my feet, he cannot walk on top of me at all.", "tokens": [51150, 407, 291, 536, 385, 406, 2684, 452, 3521, 11, 415, 2644, 1792, 322, 1192, 295, 385, 412, 439, 13, 51490], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12143798540997248, "compression_ratio": 1.580188679245283, "no_speech_prob": 0.06357917189598083}, {"id": 23, "seek": 10348, "start": 126.0, "end": 129.24, "text": " And when he does it well, then he gets a reward.", "tokens": [51490, 400, 562, 415, 775, 309, 731, 11, 550, 415, 2170, 257, 7782, 13, 51652], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12143798540997248, "compression_ratio": 1.580188679245283, "no_speech_prob": 0.06357917189598083}, {"id": 24, "seek": 12924, "start": 129.24, "end": 137.04000000000002, "text": " The other thing is normally we would like the foot to step behind the other forefoot.", "tokens": [50364, 440, 661, 551, 307, 5646, 321, 576, 411, 264, 2671, 281, 1823, 2261, 264, 661, 2091, 13498, 13, 50754], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1298724