f the little session here, he's not only more responsible for not running", "tokens": [51422, 407, 586, 538, 264, 917, 295, 264, 707, 5481, 510, 11, 415, 311, 406, 787, 544, 6250, 337, 406, 2614, 51796], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1019433617591858, "compression_ratio": 1.558252427184466, "no_speech_prob": 0.01069964561611414}, {"id": 53, "seek": 27386, "start": 273.86, "end": 279.76, "text": " over top of me, so I'm being a little more strict about him not running on top of me,", "tokens": [50364, 670, 1192, 295, 385, 11, 370, 286, 478, 885, 257, 707, 544, 10910, 466, 796, 406, 2614, 322, 1192, 295, 385, 11, 50659], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14857946742664685, "compression_ratio": 1.5288461538461537, "no_speech_prob": 0.06920497119426727}, {"id": 54, "seek": 27386, "start": 279.76, "end": 284.02000000000004, "text": " but also he is much more accustomed to the exercise.", "tokens": [50659, 457, 611, 415, 307, 709, 544, 35980, 281, 264, 5380, 13, 50872], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14857946742664685, "compression_ratio": 1.5288461538461537, "no_speech_prob": 0.06920497119426727}, {"id": 55, "seek": 27386, "start": 284.02000000000004, "end": 288.06, "text": " He has a good understanding of what's expected of him.", "tokens": [50872, 634, 575, 257, 665, 3701, 295, 437, 311, 5176, 295, 796, 13, 51074], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14857946742664685, "compression_ratio": 1.5288461538461537, "no_speech_prob": 0.06920497119426727}, {"id": 56, "seek": 27386, "start": 288.06, "end": 290.26, "text": " And there you go, perfect.", "tokens": [51074, 400, 456, 291, 352, 11, 2176, 13, 51184], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14857946742664685, "compression_ratio": 1.5288461538461537, "no_speech_prob": 0.06920497119426727}, {"id": 57, "seek": 27386, "start": 290.26, "end": 291.6, "text": " Good boy.", "tokens": [51184, 2205, 3237, 13, 51251], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14857946742664685, "compression_ratio": 1.5288461538461537, "no_speech_prob": 0.06920497119426727}, {"id": 58, "seek": 27386, "start": 291.6, "end": 297.04, "text": " So the squatting down is really working for this horse to bring his head down, which is", "tokens": [51251, 407, 264, 24305, 783, 760, 307, 534, 1364, 337, 341, 6832, 281, 1565, 702, 1378, 760, 11, 597, 307, 51523], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14857946742664685, "compression_ratio": 1.5288461538461537, "no_speech_prob": 0.06920497119426727}, {"id": 59, "seek": 29704, "start": 297.04, "end": 303.02000000000004, "text": " important for his spine to come into a neutral position and relax.", "tokens": [50364, 1021, 337, 702, 15395, 281, 808, 666, 257, 10598, 2535, 293, 5789, 13, 50663], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.19790318671693194, "compression_ratio": 1.3106060606060606, "no_speech_prob": 0.011275429278612137}, {"id": 60, "seek": 29704, "start": 303.02000000000004, "end": 306.6, "text": " And also a very obvious reward, perfect.", "tokens": [50663, 400, 611, 257, 588, 6322, 7782, 11, 2176, 13, 50842], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.19790318671693194, "compression_ratio": 1.3106060606060606, "no_speech_prob": 0.011275429278612137}, {"id": 61, "seek": 29704, "start": 306.6, "end": 309.40000000000003, "text": " One step is all you need.", "tokens": [50842, 1485, 1823, 307, 439, 291, 643, 13, 50982], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.19790318671693194, "compression_ratio": 1.3106060606060606, "no_speech_prob": 0.011275429278612137}, {"id": 62, "seek": 29704, "start": 309.40000000000003, "end": 311.16, "text": " There you have it, your first exercise.", "tokens": [50982, 821, 291, 362, 309, 11, 428, 700, 5380, 13, 51070], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.19790318671693194, "compression_ratio": 1.3106060606060606, "no_speech_prob": 0.011275429278612137}], "language": "en"}